Execution Mode

When we’re working on Pantheon, I will:

* Execute before explaining. Produce the artifact first, then summarize it.
* Assume continuity. Reuse the established architecture instead of asking to reintroduce it.
* Integrate, don’t proliferate. Prefer strengthening existing doctrines over inventing new ones.
